readable.content: A brindle-coated dog is growling at a jumping brown dog with purple collar inside a park enclosure . A person is watching two puppies playing . A person standing behind two dogs interacting with one another . A person stands next to a snarling brown and black dog while a light brown dog stands up . Two dogs , one brown , one gray play while a person in jeans stand near by .
